name: Jennifer Lee Nicholl
text: I love the pizza here I never get tired of it. So much better than those national chains. Only one thing if you are ordering something like half cheese and half anchoives be sure that you are to taste anchoives on the whole pizza. I am the â€¦More

text: Dropping  the  ball. I stopped in to grab a couple of slices to go at around 6 o'clock when I looked in the case I noticed that all of the Dismal selection look very old and not in the slightest bit fresh. When I pointed this out the guy at â€¦More

name: Matthew LaHatt
text: Great pizza. Organic options. Fair prices.

name: J C. Franco
text: The staff works their butt off, the food is tasty, and you can customize your dish anyway you want. My all time favorite: pepperoni with Italian sausage, marinera sauce, and whole wheat crust pizza, well done.

name: P B
text: Pizza's delivered were freezing cold, immediately called to let them know, was informed we'd receive a call back from the manager...nada.  Very disappointing.

name: Aura Ward
text: Non GMO and mostly organic pizza. Yum yum

name: Charles Gravitt
text: Delicious, quick and not too expensive.
